"SRC" logo stamped in runouts and "E A S T" embossed around center hole denote [l=Specialty Records Corporation] pressing. Remainder of runouts are etched, except "MASTERDISK" stamped.

Issued with printed inner sleeve with lyrics and credits.

Catalog numbers: 9 25854-1 on spine and inner sleeve, 1-25854 on the labels.

Nile Rodgers sessions (A1 to A3, B1, B4, B5):
All tracks recorded and mixed at Skyline Studios, NYC
All Nile Rodgers cuts recorded digitally and mixed analog

All tracks recorded at Dreamland Recording Studio, West Hurley, NY
Pre-production at Bearsville Studios, Bearsville, NY

Mixed at Electric Lady NYC (A4, B2)
